<h2>InPink Fashion Jewelry</h2>
    <p class="about">InPink was a fashion jewelry brand ecommerce site launched on the Magento platform. I developed several themes for the content, blog entries, product pages, landing pages optimized for conversion, and forms that delivered coupon codes integrated with mailchimp API for sign-ups.</p>
    <figure>
        <h3>Main Homepage</h3>
